{"type": "article", "id": 28942, "title": "李宇春代言 Gucci 腕表，以及，MYKITA眼镜新作不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-30T10:35:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1705, "name": "腕表"}, {"id": 8238, "name": "墨镜"}, {"id": 4780, "name": "快闪店"}, {"id": 9774, "name": "卡车"}, {"id": 29616, "name": "护发系列"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 29617, "name": "AG"}, {"id": 2120, "name": "开云"}, {"id": 21035, "name": "Wired"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 29618, "name": "MYKITA"}, {"id": 12763, "name": "Maison Margiela"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}, {"id": 2002, "name": "Balmain"}, {"id": 2175, "name": "李宇春"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 146, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703150715pNBbCLkmOidZVTHz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/06/wired-lauren-goodman-fashion\"><b><i>Wired</i> 杂志雇用首个时尚职位</b></a>｜著名的科技在线杂志<i> Wired</i> 宣布 Lauren Goodman 加入团队，担任新创立的特约时尚总监一职，这是<i> Wired </i>首次创立时尚方面的职位。Goodman 在时尚行业有 15 年的从业经验，曾在 LVMH 旗下的网站 Nowness、Style.com 、<i>Elle</i>、康泰纳仕集团的 <i>Traveler</i> 杂志等任职，为品牌 JC Penney 等提供咨询服务。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/fendi-to-launch-traveling-pop-up-concept-in-north-america-10474001/\"><b>Fendi 将开车上“快闪店”</b></a>｜奢侈品牌 Fendi 将在北美市场推出移动“快闪”的概念商店 Fendi Ape car，即在一辆复古的意大利红色三轮卡车里进行商品展示，预计在美国时间 7 月 4 日所在的周末推出。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/designer-luxury/french-court-orders-kering-pay-hedi-slimane-13-million-10475523/\"><b>法国法院裁定开云需向 Hedi Slimane 支付 1300 万美元</b></a>｜此前，Hedi Slimane 曾因未向其支付竞业禁止期间补偿而起诉前公司开云（Kering），近日，法国商业法庭裁定开云需向 Hedi Slimane 支付 1300 万美元。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://fashion.sohu.com/20160629/n456881930.shtml\"><b>李宇春成 Gucci 腕表亚洲区形象大使</b></a>｜奢侈品牌 Gucci 宣布李宇春成为品牌新任亚洲区腕表首饰形象大使，同时发布由李宇春演绎的腕表系列大片。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150652yD29FhgZBKVYvdGb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070315065379ATjbp06VX1zWYf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150654Axm2pgN6YnMvW1Rj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>1989 年，Nike 曾成立过一个全球性精英运动员俱乐部 Nike International，近日Nike <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/6/nike-sportswear-nike-international\">又为 Nike International 推出最新系列运动装</a>，以巴西里约热内卢夜晚航拍为灵感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150654hQ8Ekd6MF1oNWqUi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150655SXeFI7C1JmcAxyzw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031506555PaYH903wj62t7KC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150656XSpOUZ1IjWqNYaHP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150657FydtT92QvGmqARrx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150657ThgKCZOWaVsbq8YB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031506589co8jPIhTiFM1OJN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150659eirUlLn7PkFbazCu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n